&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Charles&amp;nbsp;Freilich&lt;/strong&gt;, Adjunct Associate Professor of Political Science, Columbia University; Senior Fellow, Harvard Belfer Center; Former Israeli Deputy National Security Advisor&lt;/p&gt;
